    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small disc provided with holes, through which a string runs. The string is wound by rotating the disc. When one pulls the string apart, the disc rotates quickly and makes a buzzing sound. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
